OL,6,FHer daughter Elizabeth was pronounced
OL,7,Fdead at her home having suffered a
OL,8,Ffractured skull and knife wounds,
OL,9,Fwhile the 50-year-old's son Ethan
OL,10,Fsuffered more than 20 sharp force
