OL,6,FJohn, who was not in court to hear the
OL,7,Fjury's findings, now faces a mandatory
OL,8,Fhospital order admitting her to
OL,9,FNottinghamshire's Rampton high
OL,10,Fsecurity hospital.
OL,12,FBefore the case was opened by the
OL,13,Fprosecution, trial judge Mr Justice
OL,14,FChoudhury explained that the jurors'
OL,15,Ftask during the expected six-day trial
OL,16,Fwould be to find whether she did the
OL,17,Facts charged against her.
OL,19,FThe judge said: "This trial is
OL,20,Fslightly unusual ` the defendant has
OL,21,Fbeen found to be under a disability.
